If you have been blessed then please take time to donate. Someone around the world needs your support and love in these trying times. Keep in mind that the mega size banks are not interested in serving the Kiva entrepreneurs. It's up to us to offer micro finance assistance to allow the loan to be funded and repaid. Whatever amount you loan has a 10x effect based on the average per capita income of your business partner.
